com.guidewire.util
Interface StringSubstitution.Exchanger

All Known Implementing Classes:
MapExchanger
Enclosing class:
StringSubstitution
public static interface StringSubstitution.Exchanger

Instance of Exchanger must be supplied to StringSubstitution. Exchanger is responsible for returning a replacement for supplied tokens found when scanning the source string.

Method Summary
 java.lang.String exchange(java.lang.String token)
          Return a string to substitute for the supplied token in the original source string.

Returns:
A string to replace the token and surrounding delimiters.
